channel.title: You need to have Java files for this Compiler to Compile. ? WHAT?!(Phonescape)
channel.description:
Hi! I made my own server a couple of weeks ago, however, it sucked! So my friend sent me his server, which he doesn't use anymore, only one problem, when I open my compiler (The Perfect Compiler version 1.6), and try to run my server it says:
You do not have Server.class. Make sure that you have used the compiler with your server BEFORE you try runing it.
So I go to compile it, then it reads:
You need to have Java files for this Compiler to Compile.
How do I fix this? Thanks.

item.title: You need to have Java files for this Compiler to Compile. ? WHAT?!(Phonescape)
item.dc:creator: @the_S0RR0W the S0RR0W
item.description:
@the_S0RR0W wrote:

Do you have Java development kit?

and do you have all the files necessary to run your server?

If not i suggest that you download a new source.
